# ANGES 1.01, reconstructing ANcestral GEnomeS maps
# July 2012.
# Contact: Cedric Chauve (Dept. Mathematics, Simon Fraser University), cedric.chauve@sfu.ca

COMMON:     general scripts used in several tasks
TREES:      scripts related to species trees
MARKERS:    scripts related to sets of markers
ACS:        scripts related to computing ACS
WEIGHT:     scripts related to weighting ACS
C1P:        scripts related to computing ancestral genomes maps using the C1P 
SERIATION:  scripts related to computing ancestral genomes maps using seriation
MASTER:     main scripts

Changes from version 1.0 to 1.01 are indicated in CHANGES files in
each directory.